        <div class="faq-answer"><p>Store-and-Forward technology keeps the POS fully functional during network outages. Transaction data is encrypted and stored locally on the iOS device, then automatically synced to Cloud HQ once connectivity is restored — preventing lost sales and data gaps. This is critical for stadiums, pop-up events, and regions with unreliable connectivity.</p></div>
